# Signature Moves

Every fighter can execute a perfect sword strike. Every wizard can cast Fireball. But only you have *your* signature move—the personal technique that defines your fighting style, bears your name, and costs less Momentum than anyone else could manage. Signature moves aren't just mechanically efficient; they're expressions of character identity made manifest in combat.

